data.description: You'll love this five bedroom Brookside home! Room for the family to roam here! You won't believe all the space until you see it. Large finished walk out basement features oversized family room/bonus room, two bedrooms and full bathroom. Spacious living room opens to the dining space and kitchen. The home has a five year old roof and 10 month old hot water heater! Fenced backyard features a storage shed, big patio space- ready for your fire pit, privacy and beautiful tree. Hang out on the deck for barbecues! So much to see here, add this one to your list!!
